title: Duplicate File Detective Professional 5.0.68 (KiwiPirate)
description:
<a href="http://www.duplicate-file-detective.com/index.htm" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.duplicate-file-detective.com/index.htm</a>


Duplicate File Detective uses state-of-the-art file content analysis technology to show you exactly where your duplicate files are (even when the file names are different). You can search multiple folders, drives, removable storage devices, even network shares - all in a single pass. Then move, zip, or remove duplicate files safely with assistance from our innovative SmartMark duplicate file selection system



INSTRUCTIONS:

Run DFD5-Setup.exe and install

Copy Patch.exe into the folder you installed to

Right Click Patch.exe -> Run as Administrator

Click Patch

Done

Run Duplicate File Detective 5

Enjoy

//KiwiPirate


NOTE: Installs on x64 & x86 but patch works on x86 ONLY
if i find a x64 patcher or keygen then i will upload that but until i do then this is only any good for x86 users
